 But one of the main reasons that people don't get what they want is that they don't figure out what that is. 

00:01:11.460 --> 00:01:14.720
 And the chance that you get what would be good for you, 

00:01:14.729 --> 00:01:20.188
 let me say, what would actually be better than what you want, right? Because, maybe you are wrong what you want, 

