 of products of status or something. That is not what I mean. I mean something like ... 

00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:51.540
 Imagine if you would take care of yourself as you would care for someone you care about and you thought, "Okay, 

00:01:51.540 --> 00:01:56.140
 I take care of this person, I would like it if everything went as well as possible for them 

00:01:56.580 --> 00:01:59.840
 What should their life be like so that it was? 

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:05.240
 Well, people don't do that. They don't sit down and think, "Okay, let me figure it out!" You have a life, 

00:02:05.250 --> 00:02:06.219
 it is difficult. 

